OverView Follow @anir0y Principles of Security Room [Free] Principles of Security Introduction The following room is going to outline some of the fundamental principles of information security. The frameworks used to protect data and systems to the elements of what exactly makes data secure.
The measures, frameworks and protocols discussed throughout this room all play a small part in &ldquo;Defence in Depth.&rdquo;
Defence in Depth is the use of multiple varied layers of security to an organisation&rsquo;s systems and data in the hopes that multiple layers will provide redundancy in an organisation&rsquo;s security perimeter.

